author: Anthony Pancia, Belinda Varischetti And Stan Shaw
title: Backpackers urged 'go home' before coronavirus lockdown
description: Augusta-Margaret River Shire president Ian Earl says backpackers "need to head to Perth and get on a plane and go home", amid mounting tensions between travellers and regional communities.
content:
Posted 
March 28, 2020 10:56:28
The head of a West Australian local council has urged backpackers to "go home" amid mounting tensions between travellers and regional communities.
